{"tid":1588995,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"以武制暴的道德基礎","createTime":"2019-09-23T05:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T04:04:28.000Z","uid":51723,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ed404e83b42c308c62023fb3fdcbfc6334f245c2","tid":1588995,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"話說最近唔少「以武制暴」的場面，有部分和理非睇到就有啲退卻<br />\n都無法嘅，香港過往嘅示威都係以和理非為主調，要一下子令「以武制暴」得到大眾認同係需要時間嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下低我就嘗試提出幾個「以武制暴」嘅道德理據比各位手足使用，方便大家去應付身邊嘅姨媽姑姐</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時想令更多人明白明白，以武制暴係道德上可以成立嘅：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 以武制暴嘅背景係黑警選擇性執法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不論7.21元朗，定係早前炮台山福建幫，事件入面都睇到黑警選擇性不執法，又或對黑社會嘅差別待遇<br />\n以武制暴嘅基礎係，<span style=\"color: red;\">本應維持社會秩序嘅執法者，不單無能力去維持社會安寧，甚至為社會帶來更大的不安全</span><br />\n<br />\n在咁嘅情況下，市民有道德義務幫手維持社會秩序<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 以武制暴並不等於私了</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好多人會誤會以武制暴就等同以暴力對待意見唔同嘅人。<span style=\"color: red;\">相反，以武制暴嘅目標，正正係止暴制亂，制服一啲使用暴力嘅人。佢哋大部分都係有武器，有機會對正表達意見嘅示威者造成威脅、甚至身體損傷嘅人。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">喺本應執法嘅黑警縱容下，呢班人極有可能、甚至造成社會不安全</span>，所以有必要以武制暴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 以武制暴係最低武力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以武制暴嘅目的係制服，唔係殺人，當中採用嘅理應係最低武力。</span>所以有唔少有足都提到，可以集中攻擊菠蘿蓋，手肘，首要目的係要令對方失去活動能力。防止其他人會受傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後想講，我哋同暴徒嘅分別，在於我哋係唔會濫用暴力。合理嘅武力係受條件制約，而唔係隨便、無理地使用。同埋亦都多謝前線手足，你哋做得好好</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望當大家受到質疑嘅時候，可以幫到大家<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"00495075230d2d705166950f949e9bbb58e70a00","tid":1588995,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"bcab78ab13def6f3afb7517f05a4c53f0abec1ed","tid":1588995,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8576ed60cc560c3051d860329bb1565c2cedda1","tid":1588995,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e42b0670dd5d673cdff61a44264eeb4fcc1028","tid":1588995,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d05d7473a43899282244d086cf32a2cc2d39af6b","tid":1588995,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d19f41b8bc2b614f672fea0d8bafc140cc286bcb","tid":1588995,"uid":220009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"推，自己香港自己救<br />\n<br />\n香港人係時候諗下建立「香港社會」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587712</a><br />\n<br />\n黃藍商戶名單(18/9更新版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577833</a>"},{"pid":"cc37da0fbfc3adc608b1a85325ba8cc6c3ff1e98","tid":1588995,"uid":191366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"612809b14e459e84881c37cf93e4f75c2bf10169","tid":1588995,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:40:56.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"93a2d664c3bb6fd1874f40fc50168c8026125972","tid":1588995,"uid":68261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"最緊要就係出師有名，道理就係同班狗一邊指住人大叫你係咪襲警一邊打9你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be1f590aa4c712af71b562d6079c22dd32adb47","tid":1588995,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:23:30.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"cee4a5bb07af513debf29e48a5a2d773fc66993c","tid":1588995,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"a43d06279ba667a7ebbd6510c9aecf7673de3266","tid":1588995,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"92106830c19358f64d9b5795f9e506e11986fea0","tid":1588995,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"你返去含啦<br />\n最低武力"},{"pid":"0b923dc7d441a9fca7d41cac8ac59b67b0500eae","tid":1588995,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:24:26.000Z","msg":"你仲有漏左<br />\n本來出手就係要震懾班人渣<br />\n等佢地知道收錢做野同有狗保護唔係大曬<br />\n係要付出重大代價<br />\n我地並唔係單純發洩 同時係保護緊自己同隊友<br />\n所以咩最低武力 咩咩規舉都係垃圾<br />\n只要唔死人就冇事<br />\n亦唔使擔心會打死人 <br />\n次次打完對家都係流下血 仍然行得走得<br />\n距離打死人仲差好遠<br />\n<br />\n你咁撚得閒做風紀<br />\n不如做下其他野貢獻下啦屌你老母<br />\n死懞撚"},{"pid":"b308e5c846c9e26cbf391cdfaed908e92c31c8ec","tid":1588995,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bad008fb28f894650f00c1d74ddfd0bb62b17cd","tid":1588995,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"【 9.28 + 10.1 】連發宣傳<br />\n<br />\n五年前的9月28日，催淚彈劃破夏愨道的半空，開展一場劍指真普選的佔領運動。<br />\n<br />\n五年過去，真普選雖仍遙遙無期，而警察比以前更黑、更暴力、更不受監管。但是，香港人履行了在當日佔領結束時許下的承諾 －「人民誓將歸來」。五年後的香港人，以更團結、更鏗鏘、更堅毅的姿態再次站到政權的面前，對抗警暴，爭取雙真普選。<br />\n<br />\n9月28日，作為一個我們都記得；我們都認為是重要的日子 － 雨傘運動五周年，我們希望和大家一同回到金鐘，在集會當中沉澱、思考。<br />\n<br />\n同時，縱然當前要舉辦一個合法的遊行是會被多番刁難，而部份手足亦已經視不反對通知書為廢紙，但我們仍入紙希望可以舉辦10.1遊行，盡力讓當日能夠有一個讓所有香港人都能夠參與的大遊行，因此約定大家，十月一日，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【 9.28 反抗威權 迎接黎明 】集會<br />\n2019年9月28日<br />\n晚上7時至9時<br />\n金鐘添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n【 10.1 沒有國慶 只有國殤 】遊行<br />\n2019年10月1日<br />\n下午兩時起步<br />\n維園集合，遊行往遮打道<br />\n<br />\n主辦︰民間人權陣線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8Dkz2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8Dkz2M.jpg&h=c7d62bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qS9jQCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqS9jQCv.jpg&h=769335de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hqy41Ka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqy41Ka.jpg&h=a6dbaf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJQZQCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJQZQCw.jpg&h=ba39fbf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a47f8bcbfd68419cdc4a3f4fa5a5cf503a6eb5c6","tid":1588995,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed404e83b42c308c62023fb3fdcbfc6334f245c2","tid":1588995,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"話說最近唔少「以武制暴」的場面，有部分和理非睇到就有啲退卻<br />\n都無法嘅，香港過往嘅示威都係以和理非為主調，要一下子令「以武制暴」得到大眾認同係需要時間嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下低我就嘗試提出幾個「以武制暴」嘅道德理據比各位手足使用，方便大家去應付身邊嘅姨媽姑姐</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時想令更多人明白明白，以武制暴係道德上可以成立嘅：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 以武制暴嘅背景係黑警選擇性執法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不論7.21元朗，定係早前炮台山福建幫，事件入面都睇到黑警選擇性不執法，又或對黑社會嘅差別待遇<br />\n以武制暴嘅基礎係，<span style=\"color: red;\">本應維持社會秩序嘅執法者，不單無能力去維持社會安寧，甚至為社會帶來更大的不安全</span><br />\n<br />\n在咁嘅情況下，市民有道德義務幫手維持社會秩序<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 以武制暴並不等於私了</span></span><br /